Vendored OpenFlexure Microscope OpenSCAD libraries
==================================================

Files in this directory (libdict.scad, utilities.scad, locking_dovetail.scad)
are taken verbatim from the OpenFlexure Microscope project:

    https://gitlab.com/openflexure/openflexure-microscope
